-- Czech Pegas Nonwovens considering issue of CZK-denominated bonds
-- 
-- Wed Sep 03, 2014 04:01AM EDT
-- None



PRAGUE, Sept 3 (Reuters) - Czech artificial textile maker Pegas Nonwovens <PGSN.PR> is considering issuing crown-denominated bonds for medium-term financing to help repay bank loans, the company said on Wednesday.

